---
title: Beef Meatball Massaman-Style Curry with Jasmine Rice and Spring Onion
description: We love good Meatball Massaman Curry with Rice  and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-meatball-massaman-style-curry-87a1b496-627d42df.jpg
